name: BEFV0-8.2
description:
You own a weird but cute Baby ErlenFire ! It's one of the Weird ones : these are black and white ErlenFires and there's only 2 of them so they're quite rare. Moreover, only 4 Baby Erlenfires have a white background. Nice Catch!
Him and « BEFV0-8.1 » are brothers but they are quite the opposite of each other. This one has a vintage, monochrome and pure look.
